of the three biggest

00:17:52.820 --> 00:17:54.170 align:middle line:90%
important factors.

00:17:54.170 --> 00:17:59.760 align:middle line:84%
Because the external environment
dictates gene expression.

00:17:59.760 --> 00:18:01.755 align:middle line:84%
So the way our genes
express themselves--

00:18:01.755 --> 00:18:03.380 align:middle line:84%
if an asteroid hit
the planet tomorrow,

00:18:03.380 --> 00:18:05.982 align:middle line:84%
