what we put in our body.

00:18:10.320 --> 00:18:12.920 align:middle line:84%
And that produces different
hormones in our body.

00:18:12.920 --> 00:18:14.561 align:middle line:90%
It changes our biochemistry.

00:18:14.561 --> 00:18:16.310 align:middle line:84%
And that changes the
internal environment,

00:18:16.310 --> 00:18:20.880 align:middle line:84%
which also affects how our
genetics express themselves.

00:18:20.880 --> 00:18:25.160 align:middle line:84%
So making very clever
choices and, really, being

00:18:25.160 --> 00:18:27.860 align:middle line:84%
sensitive to what the food's
doing inside of our body

00:18:27.860 --> 00:18:29.240 align:middle line:90%
after we've eaten it--

00:18:29.240 --> 00:18:31.700 align:middle line:84%
this will help us
understand, is this actually

00:18:31.700 --> 00:18:33.650 align:middle line:90%
serving my highest goal?

00:18:33.650 --> 00:18:37.040 align:middle line:84%
And, a lot of times,
we're so disconnected--

00:18:37.040 --> 00:18:40.260 align:middle line:84%
